{"tid":1433384,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連儂場!進!化!","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:32:16.000Z","uid":174541,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5c7f8d8ef5b36922915845a6c99b239d99407e9d","tid":1433384,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:01:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">你有每日記者會 <br />\n我有快閃連儂場</span><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現有連儂場弊病:</span><br />\n1. 加油鼓勵字句居多，受同溫層歡迎但傳播力欠奉，難以吸納中立人士<br />\n2. 死守一個位置，易受追擊破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 要真係主動行去固定位置先睇到(欠缺主動宣傳力)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">快閃連儂場設定:</span><br />\n目的: 唔怕俾人撕，但求每日update，利用時地因素將宣傳效果最大化<br />\n目標群眾: 中立 淺藍及淺黃<br />\n張貼時間: 番工前(0600至0700)及放工前(1600至2100)<br />\n地點: 人流多/等待區/廣告牌旁地方，如巴士站 地鐵入口 商場門外等<br />\n交宣方向: <br />\n1. 指出政府及警狗歪理之處，提升民智水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 以不同持分者利益角度剖釋政府禍國殃民及真普選有黎嘅好處<br />\n3. 地區性資訊，喚醒裝睡的羔羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現有連儂場改進方向:</span><br />\n1. 預留淺藍發言位置，以留言方式理論，避免同溫層效應<br />\n2. 重整各區連儂場，開拓18區連儂小組<br />\n3. 點樣可以好似街招咁實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現今要收集嘅資訊</span><br />\n1. 幸存連儂場位置<br />\n2. 被消失連儂場位置<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家需要你! 入黎傾下點樣將連儂場搞好!<br />\n首要: 快閃連儂場!<br />\n其次: 固定連儂場</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LzTqZRWC_BCmAKU1tLE37Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLzTqZRWC_BCmAKU1tLE37Q&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9ZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=bb36df4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LzTqZRWC_BCmAKU1tLE37Q</a>"},{"pid":"2db5a39297a126469e3af52470736971b88ebb51","tid":1433384,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:02:10.000Z","msg":"自推10次先"},{"pid":"a6944d8e167da7cb259db4a52fe3ee4cf5774798","tid":1433384,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946b3aefd9fe26cae2ec4b6fc46f0c25ffb125e6","tid":1433384,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1a674e36f2c9e5793e9821427721f0e859cfe2","tid":1433384,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d7e3ec616c6e1df18e288e2c267cf3cd7129e0f","tid":1433384,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ad39b5d4acbcd4b5a319ecddd484f2b43828f7","tid":1433384,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f366004fba0f66fa406862c9a3376cf468bcebbb","tid":1433384,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3dd5878b601614e7ad7ff9154b4767e94d4c80","tid":1433384,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1c213cc34ac813137dbd613f53a71cf8294062","tid":1433384,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e51a16980b7faa4a9865db29d65aea95c4a8ba","tid":1433384,"uid":78570,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:20:50.000Z","msg":"每個禮拜五, 禮拜日都係全民儲錢日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n儲錢去旅行, 投資歐美<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔好係香港燒肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劏房波話香港經濟轉差<br />\n咁香港人要儲錢來應對<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港好多黑社會可能會打劫銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係警察又怕左黑社會掉頭走喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以最好開埋外國離岸銀行戶口, 放D錢入去儲, 咁就安心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個禮拜五, 禮拜日都係全民儲錢日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n養成理財好習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家幫手係Facebook, twitter, tg wts group 做文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436759/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436759/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手正皮. 推到熱門"},{"pid":"b8255028a025e7d33f3be6e168f8520fa2d6f321","tid":1433384,"uid":223260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c7f8d8ef5b36922915845a6c99b239d99407e9d","tid":1433384,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:01:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">你有每日記者會 <br />\n我有快閃連儂場</span><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現有連儂場弊病:</span><br />\n1. 加油鼓勵字句居多，受同溫層歡迎但傳播力欠奉，難以吸納中立人士<br />\n2. 死守一個位置，易受追擊破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 要真係主動行去固定位置先睇到(欠缺主動宣傳力)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">快閃連儂場設定:</span><br />\n目的: 唔怕俾人撕，但求每日update，利用時地因素將宣傳效果最大化